{"tid":1671466,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【Més que un Club】希望聽晚大家著住巴塞波衫出黎","createTime":"2019-10-23T13:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T14:24:57.000Z","uid":22099,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"733e36327b65414285a080d9b30c7076c73b8f3e","tid":1671466,"uid":22099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:21:21.000Z","msg":"大家成日話鍾意巴塞，知唔知我地球會既格言係「<span style=\"color: red;\">M&eacute;s</span>　<span style=\"color: blue;\">que</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">un</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">Club</span>」，知唔知道呢句說話背後既球會精神係乜野？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTcNxRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTcNxRu.jpg&h=11f421ae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圖為在加泰民選政治官員因舉辦前途公投而被西班牙政府以叛亂罪下獄後</span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">巴塞球迷在魯營球場高舉「自由」標語及加泰旗的一幕。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家成日話撐巴塞，知唔知我地球會既家鄉加泰隆尼亞依家同香港一樣面對緊警暴？知唔知好多我地既球迷係巴塞羅那既街頭日日畀警察打？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uw16OuN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUw16OuN.png&h=eacd92b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/tsunami_dem/status/1183823734735622145?fbclid=IwAR1ShA-mcH0H6YEEa8CZ40M5uilJJ4tOY-Yf_f--e0fHk649fQ3uJMoWgcU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftsunami_dem%2Fstatus%2F1183823734735622145%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ShA-mcH0H6YEEa8CZ40M5uilJJ4tOY-Yf_f--e0fHk649fQ3uJMoWgcU&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yHbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=fbed9173\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftsunami_dem%2Fstatus%2F1183823734735622145%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ShA-mcH0H6YEEa8CZ40M5uilJJ4tOY-Yf_f--e0fHk649fQ3uJMoWgcU&h=c9538290\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tsunami_dem/status/1183823734735622145?fbclid=IwAR1ShA-mcH0H6YEEa8CZ40M5uilJJ4tOY-Yf_f--e0fHk649fQ3uJMoWgcU</a></span><br />\n其實連哥迪奧拿都出左聲，譴責西班牙政府暴力鎮壓加泰人和平示威，希望西班牙政府尊重加泰人民既自由，促請西班牙政府尋求政治同民主既方式，同加泰人民展開對話。<br />\n<br />\n我知呢幾日CC台好多人係咁叫大家唔好撐加泰，仲有人開口埋口加泰狗。我唔知其他人點睇，但你問我，呢個世界並冇人叫加泰狗，只有一班球迷叫<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">狗</span>，而我好希望我地呢班<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">狗</span>，就算唔去聽晚個加泰集會都好，千祈唔好同加泰割蓆。大家同加泰割蓆，其實就係同巴塞割蓆。我更加希望大家，能夠畀多少少時間，理解下我地球會背後既血汗同歷史，理解下巴塞同埋加泰抗爭之間既關係，理解下咩叫「<span style=\"color: red;\">M&eacute;s</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">que</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">un</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">Club</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n聽晚七點鐘，遮打花園，希望各位手足會黎加泰集會，我地著住巴塞球衣相認。<br />\n<br />\n／／係巴塞令我知道足球唔單只係足球，而係一種愛。<br />\n<br />\n想當年，睇住細哨著住紅藍雙間嘅波衫踢波。原本件波衫面乜都無，唔似其他球隊上面有心口贊助；有一日，件衫心口上面多咗幾個英文字：unicef，聯合國兒童基金會。<br />\n<br />\n其他隊嘅作客波衫好型，但唔知點解巴塞個件要係紅黃間。原來紅黃間係巴塞所屬嘅加泰羅尼亞嘅旗幟顏色，巴塞 more than a club ，因為佢係西班牙中央政府打壓當地文化時，佢守護緊屬於佢哋嘅價值。／／<span style=\"font-size: small;\">《係巴塞令我知道甚麼叫做愛》<a href=\"https://sportsyeah.hk/2019/10/22/%e4%bf%82%e5%b7%b4%e5%a1%9e%e4%bb%a4%e6%88%91%e7%9f%a5%e9%81%93%e7%94%9a%e9%ba%bc%e5%8f%ab%e5%81%9a%e6%84%9b-hong-kong-catalonia-solidarity-assembly/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportsyeah.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F22%2F%25e4%25bf%2582%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e5%25a1%259e%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e6%2588%2591%25e7%259f%25a5%25e9%2581%2593%25e7%2594%259a%25e9%25ba%25bc%25e5%258f%25ab%25e5%2581%259a%25e6%2584%259b-hong-kong-catalonia-solidarity-assembly%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yHbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=4f308c7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://sportsyeah.hk/2019/10/22/%e4%bf%82%e5%b7%b4%e5%a1%9e%e4%bb%a4%e6%88%91%e7%9f%a5%e9%81%93%e7%94%9a%e9%ba%bc%e5%8f%ab%e5%81%9a%e6%84%9b-hong-kong-catalonia-solidarity-assembly/</a></span>"},{"pid":"f32ccddd4df40f8d0d290a450f542dfff3f2e9f9","tid":1671466,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得巴9有巴塞波衫"},{"pid":"cb0a50f6cefb815be3e5359d194cde9fef6f3be7","tid":1671466,"u